    "media:imagetext": "ROCKY MOUNTAIN\nAIRWAYS\nRA\nTM\nUNITED AIRLINES\nJOINT TIMETABLE\nEFFECTIVE JULY 2, 1981\n• LAMbOAT OPHINGS\nVAIL/AVON/BEAVER CREEK\nASPEN/SNOWMASS\nCOLORADO\nSPRINGS\nALAMOSA\nSERVING:\nDENVER\nALAMOSA\nASPEN/SNOWMASS\nCHEYENNE\nCOLORADO SPRINGS\nLARAMIE\nSTEAMBOAT SPRINGS\nVAIL/AVON/BEAVER CREEK\nVisiting new markets, or just visiting …make the\nconnection via United Airlines and Rocky Mountain Airways.\n• More than 86 flights daily.\n• Frequent flights mean minimum layovers.\n• Turbo-prop De Havilland Dash-7 and Twin Otter aircraft.\n1999.047.448",
